725871f-a.text:
144th Avenue, north side, west from 184th Street, showing new type houses, contrasting sharply with the old farmhouses still remaining along the south side of the avenue.
P. L. Sperr  March 19, 1927

725872f.text:
144th Avenue, south side, at 184th Street, showing old type farm houses before the area was developed into a residential neighborhood.

PL. Sperr  March 19, 1927
